p.k: Greg Holder, from a rival job centre, convinces Trish to try out a new way with the job centre, based on relaxation and filling the centre with bean bags. Trish is smitten with Greg and does everything he says, but is he all he seems? (2015). Cast: Sarah Hadland, Russell Tovey, Jo Enright, Laura Aikman. Director: Sasha Ransome.
